caption: Yep, this is me. Living my best life in a vat of butter. Just kidding, I’m in a bathtub full of balls. 🛁 Either way, LIFE IS GOOD!! Just a friendly reminder to do things YOUR WAY! You’re awesome, you deserve it. Don’t give a* about what anyone else thinks, let them do it their way, too. Love yourself and each other best you can. Share laughs, follow your bliss, and make all the moments count. And if you want to, EAT ALL THE BUTTER!! 🥞✨💝🙏🏻 p.s. Chi-town friends, @wearehappyplace is still open for two more weeks. Check. It. Out. 😉

Oh hi!! Sending everyone a big ball of sunshine cuz I love ya so darn much! ☀️💝🎊 Also, wanna say Happy Teacher Appreciation Day to so many teacher friends and fam, you guys help make the world a better place! 🌎👍🏻 My sweet friend @hotpinkpineapples tagged me to share my favorite teacher- 2nd Grade, Ms. Ohstrom. She had a piano in her classroom and we got to sing everyday and IT WAS MAGIC! 😭🎹💖🎊 photo cred. @hotpinkpineapples luv u girl! #dedicateanapple#whpcolorpop

‘Curz sometimes you just need a big ol piece of cake to get you to humpday! 🍰💯 Just about to rewatch @santaclaritadiet before the new season comes out, also taking recs on any new fun shows if somebody’s got em? “-the smell of roasting coffee and burnt sugar and melting chocolate and mint and violets and crushed hazelnuts and apple blossom and caramel and lemon peel...” ☕️🍫🌸🍋🍭 Eeeeeeee!! SWEETEST words from my fav childhood book, “Charlie and the Chocolate Factory”, it sparked my imagination and forever filled me with wonder! 
The love of reading awesome books is something I’m so happy I can pass on to my kiddo, which is why I’m OVERJOYED to be a part of @pizzahut’s Literacy Project Fundraising Campaign! It raises money to provide kids in need with access to books and educational resources so that they can create lasting memories, we can help by visiting the link to donate! 
And I’d LOVE to hear what your favorite childhood book is! Share a photo with your book and use the hashtags #HelpStartANewChapter and #sweepstakes, and you’ll be entered to win an all-expenses paid trip to bring your childhood book to life!! 📚✨🌈💝✨🤗 #pizzahutpartner
